videos.description: North Carolina's Theo Pinson makes the huge block on Arkansas' Anton Beard.
videos.headline: Pinson sends shot into stands

videos.description: North Carolina's Theo Pinson makes the great bounce pass to Sterling Manley, who hits the hook shot.
videos.headline: Manley finishes off the great pass

videos.description: North Carolina's Luke Maye blocks Arkansas' Anton Beard and keep the Tar Heels ' defense thriving.
videos.headline: Maye makes solid block

videos.description: North Carolina's Luke Maye hits the 3-pointer to help the Tar Heels' offense going into halftime.
videos.headline: Maye hits turnaround 3-pointer

videos.description: North Carolina's Luke Maye stays hot offensively with another 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Maye hits deep three

videos.description: North Carolina's Theo Pinson makes a strong block and Kenny William's gets blocked by Arkansas' Jaylen Barford, but Brandon Robinson is there for the putback.
videos.headline: Arkansas and North Carolina trade blocks

videos.description: North Carolina's Theo Pinson slams down the huge one-handed dunk to help pad the lead for the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: Pinson throws down monster slam

videos.description: North Carolina's Luke Maye hits his fourth 3-pointer of the game en route to a career-high 28 points.
videos.headline: Maye hits another three

videos.description: Bill Walton and Roxy Bernstein analyze North Carolina's Luke Maye's strong offensive performance against Arkansas.
videos.headline: Maye spurs Tar Heels in victory
